{"id":2468,"date":"2021-06-25T08:52:30","date_gmt":"2021-06-25T08:52:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/?p=2468"},"modified":"2021-06-25T08:52:32","modified_gmt":"2021-06-25T08:52:32","slug":"quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang\/","title":{"rendered":"Quy tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nh\u1ea5t"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Quy tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. H\u00e3y ngh\u0129 th\u1eed xem\u2026 M\u1ed9t \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng b\u1ecb b\u1ecf qua, thanh to\u00e1n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n sai \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng b\u1ef1c t\u1ee9c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 m\u00e0 doanh nghi\u1ec7p kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, 65% kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd r\u1eddi b\u1ecf th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u ch\u1ec9 trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1eb7p s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t quy tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng tr\u01a1n tru cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Sau \u0111\u00e2y, LAMECO s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 quy tr\u00ecnh n\u00e0y. H\u00e3y ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_17 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal ez-toc-grey\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">M\u1ee5c l\u1ee5c n\u1ed9i dung<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: none;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"><\/i><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang\/#Quan_ly_xu_ly_don_hang_la_gi\" title=\"Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\">Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang\/#Tai_sao_ban_can_xu_ly_don_hang_mot_cach_chinh_xac\" title=\"T\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c?\">T\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c?<\/a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang\/#Tranh_thua_va_thieu_hang\" title=\"Tr\u00e1nh th\u1eeba v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu h\u00e0ng\">Tr\u00e1nh th\u1eeba v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu h\u00e0ng<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang\/#Giam_thieu_sai_lam_khi_hoan_thanh_don_hang\" title=\"Gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u sai l\u1ea7m khi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng\">Gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u sai l\u1ea7m khi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang\/#Thong_tin_dang_tin_cay_ho_tro_ra_quyet_dinh\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh\">Th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang\/#Giam_lang_phi_thoi_gian\" title=\"Gi\u1ea3m l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed th\u1eddi gian\">Gi\u1ea3m l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed th\u1eddi gian<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang\/#Quy_trinh_xu_ly_don_hang\" title=\"Quy tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng\">Quy tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng<\/a><ul class=\"ez-toc-list-level-3\"><li class=\"ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang\/#Khach_hang_dat_hang\" title=\"Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng\">Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang\/#Xac_nhan_don_hang\" title=\"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng\">X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang\/#Dong_goi\" title=\"\u0110\u00f3ng g\u00f3i\">\u0110\u00f3ng g\u00f3i<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang\/#Van_chuyen\" title=\"V\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n\">V\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang\/#Thanh_toan\" title=\"Thanh to\u00e1n\">Thanh to\u00e1n<\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang\/#Doi_tra_hang\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed5i tr\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng\">\u0110\u1ed5i tr\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quan_ly_xu_ly_don_hang_la_gi\"><\/span>Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh nh\u1eadn, theo d\u00f5i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u khi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0 k\u1ebft th\u00fac khi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Khi doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u00e0ng m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng quy m\u00f4, t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u00f3a v\u00e0 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp h\u1ee3p l\u00fd quy tr\u00ecnh n\u00e0y c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, quy m\u00f4 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb qu\u00e1 t\u1ea3i v\u00ec s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"535\" src=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-3-1024x535.jpg\" alt=\"Quy tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng\" class=\"wp-image-2470\" srcset=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-3-1024x535.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-3-300x157.jpg 300w, https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-3-768x401.jpg 768w, https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-3.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tai_sao_ban_can_xu_ly_don_hang_mot_cach_chinh_xac\"><\/span>T\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tri\u1ec3n khai h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 h\u01a1i qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c khi b\u1ea1n \u0111ang \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh doanh nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m nh\u1ecf. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t doanh nghi\u1ec7p l\u1edbn c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u1eebng \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t. Sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1eed l\u00fd v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tranh_thua_va_thieu_hang\"><\/span>Tr\u00e1nh th\u1eeba v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu h\u00e0ng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n h\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n kho cao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n th\u1eeba ho\u1eb7c thi\u1ebfu h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a. Th\u1eeba h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadp th\u00eam h\u00e0ng m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1n cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Thi\u1ebfu h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m doanh s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch tr\u01a1n tru c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap l\u00e0m t\u0103ng t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n h\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n kho. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nguy c\u01a1 thi\u1ebfu ho\u1eb7c th\u1eeba h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Giam_thieu_sai_lam_khi_hoan_thanh_don_hang\"><\/span>Gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u sai l\u1ea7m khi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sai l\u1ea7m khi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng khi b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i chu\u1ea9n, in nh\u00e3n v\u00e0 g\u1eedi ch\u00fang \u0111i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ng\u00e0y nay, \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y t\u1eeb c\u00e1c k\u00eanh b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng kh\u00e1c nhau. Trong l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c v\u00e0 nh\u1eafn tin h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ho\u00e0n ti\u1ec1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"535\" src=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-2-1024x535.jpg\" alt=\"Quy tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng\" class=\"wp-image-2469\" srcset=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-2-1024x535.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-2-300x157.jpg 300w, https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-2-768x401.jpg 768w, https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-2.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p cao. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u1ed7i, sai \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9, v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n ch\u1eadm tr\u1ec5,&#8230; c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c t\u1edbi danh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ed1i \u01b0u quy tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng ngay t\u1ea1i doanh nghi\u1ec7p. C\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u00f3a v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 h\u00f3a gi\u00fap l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 r\u1ee7i ro do con ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i sai l\u1ec7ch m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng doanh nghi\u1ec7p m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb qu\u00e1 t\u1ea3i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Thong_tin_dang_tin_cay_ho_tro_ra_quyet_dinh\"><\/span>Th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y d\u1eef li\u1ec7u \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng ngay t\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7, l\u00e0m cho vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e2n t\u00edch c\u00e1c d\u1eef li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u0169ng gi\u00fap cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 theo th\u1eddi gian th\u1ef1c b\u1edfi v\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 quy tr\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Giam_lang_phi_thoi_gian\"><\/span>Gi\u1ea3m l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed th\u1eddi gian<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Khi b\u1ea1n \u0111ang \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t doanh nghi\u1ec7p th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c nh\u01b0 doanh nh\u00e2n, nh\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a ra t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed7i gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian cho vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n doanh nghi\u1ec7p th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ho\u1eb7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u. Cho n\u00ean quy tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng tr\u01a1n tru c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"535\" src=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-6-1024x535.jpg\" alt=\"Quy tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng\" class=\"wp-image-2473\" srcset=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-6-1024x535.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-6-300x157.jpg 300w, https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-6-768x401.jpg 768w, https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-6.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quy_trinh_xu_ly_don_hang\"><\/span>Quy tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Quy tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy tr\u00ecnh kh\u00e9p k\u00edn, b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng mua s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e2u v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng. Quy tr\u00ecnh y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ph\u1ea7n, th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi nhau \u0111\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Khach_hang_dat_hang\"><\/span>Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u01a1n \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u n\u01a1i t\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00f4ng qua nhi\u1ec1u k\u00eanh b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng. \u0110\u1ec3 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp quy tr\u00ecnh h\u1ee3p l\u00fd t\u1eeb kh\u00e2u k\u0129 thu\u1eadt, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u0111a k\u00eanh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u tr\u1eef nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean quan nh\u01b0 chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng, chi ti\u1ebft v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n, \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eadn h\u00e0ng\u2026 t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng online.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Xac_nhan_don_hang\"><\/span>X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 thu th\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i chi\u1ebfu \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 trong kho. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng. N\u1ebfu h\u1ebft h\u00e0ng, b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn k\u1ecbp th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o l\u1ea1i cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng. Qua \u0111\u00f3, tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ea5u t\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dong_goi\"><\/span>\u0110\u00f3ng g\u00f3i<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t khi \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn, th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m sao cho \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft v\u00e0 g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng. Kh\u00e2u \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i c\u0169ng quan tr\u1ecdng, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 nguy\u00ean v\u1eb9n c\u1ee7a s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"535\" src=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-4-1024x535.jpg\" alt=\"Quy tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng\" class=\"wp-image-2471\" srcset=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-4-1024x535.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-4-300x157.jpg 300w, https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-4-768x401.jpg 768w, https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-4.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Van_chuyen\"><\/span>V\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i in nh\u00e3n s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Hi\u1ec7n nay, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m cho ph\u00e9p doanh nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n. Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u r\u1ee7i ro khi giao h\u00e0ng t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Thanh_toan\"><\/span>Thanh to\u00e1n<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau khi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi b\u01b0\u1edbc thanh to\u00e1n. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thanh to\u00e1n qua Internet Banking. H\u00e3y l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 tin c\u1eady cao, b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng \u01b0ng \u00fd v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n ti\u1ec1n (n\u1ebfu kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng thanh to\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc).&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Doi_tra_hang\"><\/span>\u0110\u1ed5i tr\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00f3 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft lu\u00f4n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1ea3 v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n ti\u1ec1n? Ho\u00e0n tr\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed v\u00e0 x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng. N\u1ebfu kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi quy tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng th\u00ec h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd mua s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5y th\u00eam l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o n\u1eefa.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u1ed1c r\u1ec5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 logistic.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"535\" src=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-5-1024x535.jpg\" alt=\"Quy tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng\" class=\"wp-image-2472\" srcset=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-5-1024x535.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-5-300x157.jpg 300w, https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-5-768x401.jpg 768w, https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/quy-trinh-xu-ly-don-hang-5.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Quy tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng t\u1ed1i \u01b0u l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i doanh nghi\u1ec7p. Quy tr\u00ecnh k\u00e9m s\u1ebd l\u00e0m doanh nghi\u1ec7p g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i trong qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t doanh nghi\u1ec7p n\u00e0o mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1eafc m\u1eafc n\u00e0o, \u0111\u1eebng ng\u1ea1i li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi LAMECO. H\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u00f4ng qua website <a href=\"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"52\">LAMECO <\/a>ho\u1eb7c fanpage <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/lameco.group\">LAMECO<\/a> \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Quy tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. H\u00e3y ngh\u0129 th\u1eed xem\u2026 M\u1ed9t \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng b\u1ecb b\u1ecf qua, thanh to\u00e1n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n sai \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng b\u1ef1c t\u1ee9c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 m\u00e0 [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":2474,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[10,15],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2468"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2468"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2468\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2474"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/lameco.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2468"}],"wp:term":